Teltoli grabbed hold of Carnage with her paws and held tight as she tilted her wings upwards, and caught a thermal. Carnage was about 2 meters off the ground before they suddenly zoomed up, thanks to the warm rising air under her wings. Slowly but surely the were making it to the island!

"Okay, this is probably the weirdest sight and thing I have ever done, and I bet it looks real weird too, but you can open your eyes Carnage!"

Seeing the raptor keep her eyes firmly closed, she sighs and concentrates on getting to the island.

"There must be a battle, I can see laser shots.." she stops as one array of shots goes everywhere "Woah! Someone's going crazy!" She laughs

Suddenly the thermal drops, and Teltoli feels a jolt. Oh great the thermal had stopped, but they were only 100 meters away, they were going to make it!
